These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, house, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, japanese, american, german
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, magic-tricks, chess
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the fan of house##1
 3. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 8. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
10. the german is somewhere to the right of the american##5
11. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | r&b   | house    |
| Nationality           | american       | german   | japanese   | thai     |
| Hobby     | dancing       | fishing | chess  | magic-tricks      |

