.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, daisy, lily
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, manager, software-developer, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
 2. the software-developer is in an odd position##4
 3. the mechanic is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the manager##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growslily and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the manager is the person who growslily##1
10. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Flower   | rose      | dahlia       | lily | daisy |
| Job           | software-developer       | mechanic    | manager     | accountant         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

