.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, rock-climbing, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
City: colone, prague, london, new-york
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 9. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person traveling to colone##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | puzzles    | rock-climbing      | photography   | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | horror | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| City           | london      | colone          | new-york | prague  |

