.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, fuchsia, azure, apricot
City: marseilles, berlin, rome, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, tennis
 1. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person traveling to berlin and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Color           | fuchsia    | apricot   | azure | ivory |
| City   | venice      | berlin    | marseilles        | rome         |
| Sport         | baseball    | lacrosse | tennis         | handball    |

