 9. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
10. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

