The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person driving the bus is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person driving the boat##2
 4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Game          | backgammon    | poker        | monopoly     | go          |
| Transport           | quad-bike | skateboard        | bus | boat |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

