.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, parkour, weightlifting
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, classical, pop, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the fan of country##2
 6. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the fan of classical##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | parkour   | weightlifting      | baseball | cricket     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | country     | pop      | classical   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, drawing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
City: paris, boston, miami, liverpool
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 7. the social-worker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | filmmaking | drawing  | video-games    | writing       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| City   | liverpool      | miami    | boston        | paris |

 